## Internationalization (i18n)

### File Structure
```
src/
  locales/
    en/
      common.json
    es/
      common.json
```

### Key Conventions
- Snake_case keys (`welcome_message`).
- Avoid concatenated strings; use interpolation (`{{name}}`).

### Fallback Strategy
- Default locale `en`; fallback chain defined in config.

### Runtime
- Use `next-i18next` or `react-intl` provider.
- Detect locale via `Accept-Language` header or user preference.

### Testing
- Unit test missing keys (`i18n-tester`), fail CI if untranslated.
